reviewText: This is nicely done.  Great sound, great packaging ... I wish I had been there and this is the next best thing.

The Video quality is very poor, the camera is always fixed without zooming. G Govan in most of the video is not displayed on the scene because the camera is static and distant.
It's a shame that this kind of videos are included in a boxset. However the quality of the musicians is very good ..... As a fan of GPS and AFJP is a shame to have this video.
